{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"1 Par les vents soufflant sans cesse en rafales !","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:2","price":"2 Par les vents se déchaînant impétueusement !","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:3","price":"3 Par les anges qui déploient les livres révélés !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:4","price":"4 Par les anges qui apportent ce qui distingue le vrai du faux !","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:5","price":"5 Par les anges qui transmettent aux Messagers la Révélation,","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:6","price":"6 enlevant toute excuse aux hommes et leur servant d’avertissement !","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:7","price":"7 Ce qui vous est promis s’accomplira inéluctablement.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:8","price":"8 Et ce, lorsque les étoiles seront éteintes","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:9","price":"9 et lorsque le ciel sera fendu,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:10","price":"10 que les montagnes seront pulvérisées","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:11","price":"11 et que les Messagers seront rassemblés.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:12","price":"12 Mais pour quel jour cet événement a-t-il été fixé ?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:13","price":"13 Pour le Jour du jugement dernier.","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:14","price":"14 Qui pourrait t’indiquer ce qu’est vraiment le Jour du jugement dernier ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:15","price":"15 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:16","price":"16 N’avons-Nous pas anéanti les peuples impies du passé ?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:17","price":"17 Nous réservons le même sort à ceux qui leur ont succédé.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:18","price":"18 C’est ainsi que Nous traitons ceux qui vivent dans l’impiété.","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:19","price":"19 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:20","price":"20 Ne vous avons-Nous pas créés d’un vulgaire liquide","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:21","price":"21 que Nous avons déposé dans un réceptacle sûr[1527],","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1527] La matrice de la femme.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:22","price":"22 pour une période bien déterminée ?","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:23","price":"23 Par Notre pouvoir absolu, l’avons-Nous ainsi décrété.","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:24","price":"24 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:25","price":"25 N’avons-Nous pas fait de la terre le séjour","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:26","price":"26 des vivants tout comme celui des morts ?","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:27","price":"27 N’y avons-Nous pas planté des monts altiers et placé pour votre consommation une eau particulièrement douce ?","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:28","price":"28 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:29","price":"29 « Allez donc vers le châtiment que vous traitiez de mensonge !","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:30","price":"30 Allez vous abriter sous la fumée de l’Enfer s’élevant en trois colonnes,","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:31","price":"31 ni capable de vous faire de l’ombre, ni de vous protéger des flammes. »","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:32","price":"32 Le Feu projettera des étincelles aussi grosses que des tours[1528],","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1528] Ou : des troncs d’arbres.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:33","price":"33 à l’image de chameaux de couleur noire[1529].","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1529] Ou : jaune. Autre sens : à l’image des cordages d’un bateau.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:34","price":"34 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:35","price":"35 Ce Jour-là, les impies ne pourront s’exprimer,","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:36","price":"36 pas plus qu’il ne leur sera permis de s’excuser.","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:37","price":"37 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:38","price":"38 « Voici le Jour du jugement dernier. Nous vous avons réunis, vous et vos devanciers.","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:39","price":"39 Si vous avez les moyens d’échapper au châtiment, alors employez-les ! »","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:40","price":"40 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:41","price":"41 Les pieux croyants, quant à eux, seront sous d’épais ombrages, au milieu de sources vives,","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:42","price":"42 dégustant les fruits les plus désirables.","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:43","price":"43 « Mangez et buvez en paix pour prix de vos œuvres passées ! »","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:44","price":"44 C’est ainsi que Nous récompenserons ceux qui auront vécu dans la piété.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:45","price":"45 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:46","price":"46 « Mangez[1530] et jouissez quelque temps de cette vie dans votre impiété ! »","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1530] Vous, mécréants !","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:47","price":"47 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:48","price":"48 Lorsqu’on leur demande de s’incliner en prière, ils s’y refusent avec fierté.","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:49","price":"49 Malheur, ce Jour-là, à ceux qui auront rejeté la vérité !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:50","price":"50 En quel livre croiront-ils, s’ils ne croient pas en celui-ci ?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}